data.description: You don't have to do anything but move in!! This home is in perfect, model home condition!! Better than new!!! This beautiful townhome is in mint condition and move in ready! Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, Silver Comet Trail and the interstate. This home offers an open concept floor plan with tons of natural lighting and neutral colors, gorgeous kitchen with huge island, beautiful cabinets with tons of space, stone countertops and stainless steal appliances and lovely wood laminate floors throughout the main level. Spacious living room with gas log fireplace and dining area. Upstairs you will find a large loft for extra living space and spacious bedrooms. Huge master suite with trey ceilings and sitting area. Large master bath with seperate tile shower and tub, double vanity and walk in closet. Townhome also has a patio and backyard off the main level. Yard can be fenced if buyer chooses to do so. Neighborhood also includes swimming, clubhouse and playground. Call for easy showing today!
